trans-unit.source: Defines a set of <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.CommandID"></xref> fields that each correspond to a command function provided by the host environment.
trans-unit.target: Definisce un set di <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.CommandID"> </xref> campi che ognuno corrisponde a una funzione di comando fornita dall'ambiente host.

trans-unit.source: MenuCommands contains a set of <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CommandID> fields that can be used to specify a command to link when adding a command using the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IMenuCommandService.AddCommand%2A> method of the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IMenuCommandService>.
trans-unit.target: Oggetti MenuCommand contiene un set di <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CommandID>campi che possono essere utilizzati per specificare un comando da collegare al momento dell'aggiunta di un comando utilizzando il <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IMenuCommandService.AddCommand%2A>metodo di <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IMenuCommandService>.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IMenuCommandService> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IMenuCommandService.AddCommand%2A> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CommandID>
